<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SYUR — Propuesta Comercial · [NOMBRE DEL PROYECTO]</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400;500&family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;0,9..40,700;1,9..40,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
:root {
  --negro:    #0A0A0A;
  --blanco:   #FFFFFF;
  --azul:     #1A6BFF;
  --azul-md:  #3D85FF;
  --rojo:     #FF2D2D;
  --naranja:  #FF5A1A;
  --gris:     #666666;
  --gris-cl:  #F4F4F4;
  --gris-osc: #111111;
  --border:   #E0E0E0;
  --lblue:    #AACCFF;
  --font-d:   'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
  --font-b:   'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  --font-m:   'DM Mono', monospace;
}

*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body { font-family: var(--font-b); background: #111; color: var(--negro); overflow-x: hidden; }

/* ── PROGRESS BAR ── */
.progress-bar {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0;
  height: 2px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--naranja), var(--azul));
  z-index: 200;
  transition: width 0.1s ease;
  width: 0%;
}

/* ── NAV DOTS ── */
.nav-dots {
  position: fixed; right: 28px; top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;
  z-index: 100;
}
.nav-dot {
  width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s ease;
  border: none; padding: 0;
}
.nav-dot.active { background: var(--azul); transform: scale(1.4); }

/* ── SHARED ── */
section { min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; padding: 80px 60px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }

.star-shape {
  display: inline-block;
  width: var(--sz, 20px); height: var(--sz, 20px);
  background: currentColor;
  clip-path: polygon(50% 0%,55% 45%,100% 50%,55% 55%,50% 100%,45% 55%,0% 50%,45% 45%);
}

.label {
  font-family: var(--font-b);
  font-weight: 700; font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
}

.grain {
  position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none;
  opacity: 0.03;
  background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  background-size: 128px; mix-blend-mode: overlay;
}

.reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(32px); transition: opacity 0.9s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1), transform 0.9s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1); }
.reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
.reveal-d1 { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
.reveal-d2 { transition-delay: 0.22s; }
.reveal-d3 { transition-delay: 0.36s; }
.reveal-d4 { transition-delay: 0.5s; }

@keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity:0; transform: translateY(20px); } to { opacity:1; transform: none; } }
@keyframes fadeIn { from{opacity:0} to{opacity:1} }
@keyframes lineGrow { from { transform: scaleY(0); transform-origin: top; } to { transform: scaleY(1); transform-origin: top; } }
@keyframes starIn { from { transform: scale(0) rotate(-45deg); opacity:0; } to { transform: scale(1) rotate(0); opacity:1; } }

/* ══════════════════════════════════════
   1. CARÁTULA
══════════════════════════════════════ */
#caratula {
  background: var(--negro);
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 48px 64px;
  min-height: 100vh;
  align-items: stretch;
}

#caratula .red-line {
  position: absolute; left: 64px; top: 8%; bottom: 8%;
  width: 3px; background: var(--rojo);
  animation: lineGrow 1.2s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1) 0.2s both;
}

#caratula .blue-block {
  position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; bottom: 15%; width: 52%;
  clip-path: polygon(22% 0%, 100% 0%, 100% 42%, 22% 0%);
  background: var(--azul);
}
#caratula .blue-block::after {
  content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background: var(--azul-md);
  clip-path: polygon(50% 0%, 100% 0%, 100% 68%, 50% 0%);
}

#caratula .gradient-line {
  position: absolute; left: 64px; bottom: 17%;
  width: 42%; height: 3px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--naranja), var(--azul));
}

#caratula .s1 { position:absolute; right:26%; top:22%; color:var(--blanco); --sz:28px; animation: starIn 0.7s cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1) 0.8s both; }
#caratula .s2 { position:absolute; right:10%; top:48%; color:var(--lblue); --sz:12px; animation: starIn 0.6s cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1) 1s both; }
#caratula .s3 { position:absolute; left:44%; bottom:8%; color:rgba(255,255,255,.15); --sz:7px; animation: starIn 0.5s ease 1.2s both; }

#caratula .cover-content {
  position: relative; z-index: 2;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  flex: 1; justify-content: center;
  align-items: flex-start;
  padding-left: 36px;
  max-width: 680px;
}

#caratula .cover-label {
  font-family: var(--font-b); font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  color: var(--azul); margin-bottom: 28px;
  animation: fadeUp 1s ease 0.4s both;
}

#caratula h1 {
  font-family: var(--font-d);
  font-size: clamp(64px, 8vw, 100px);
  line-height: 0.92; color: var(--blanco);
  letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  animation: fadeUp 1s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1) 0.5s both;
}

#caratula .year-row {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;
  margin-top: 28px;
  animation: fadeUp 1s ease 0.7s both;
}
#caratula .year {
  font-family: var(--font-b); font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 26px; color: var(--azul); letter-spacing: 0.06em;
}
#caratula .red-rule { width: 72px; height: 3px; background: var(--rojo); }

/* Footer carátula */
#caratula .cover-footer {
  position: relative; z-index: 2; width: 100%;
  border-top: 0.5px solid #1e1e1e;
  padding-top: 20px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-end;
  animation: fadeIn 1s ease 0.9s both;
}

#caratula .cover-date {
  font-family: var(--font-m); font-size: 8px;
  color: #3a3a3a; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
}

/* ══════════════════════════════════════
   2. OBJETIVOS
══════════════════════════════════════ */
#objetivos {
  background: var(--blanco);
  align-items: flex-start;
  padding: 100px 120px;
  border-bottom: 3px solid transparent;
  border-image: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--naranja), var(--azul)) 1;
}

#objetivos .obj-number {
  position: absolute; right: 80px; top: 80px;
  font-family: var(--font-d); font-size: 180px;
  color: rgba(0,0,0,0.03); line-height: 1; pointer-events: none;
}

#objetivos .obj-label { color: var(--azul); margin-bottom: 20px; }

#objetivos h2 {
  font-family: var(--font-d);
  font-size: clamp(42px, 5vw, 68px);
  color: var(--negro); line-height: 0.95;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em; margin-bottom: 40px; max-width: 600px;
}

#objetivos .obj-body {
  font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75;
  color: var(--gris); max-width: 560px; margin-bottom: 48px;
}

#objetivos .obj-red-accent {
  position: absolute; left: 0; top: 50%;
  width: 3px; height: 80px;
  background: var(--rojo); transform: translateY(-50%);
}

/* Logo cliente en objetivos */
#objetivos .logos-row {
  display: flex; align-items: flex-start;
  flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;
  margin-bottom: 56px;
}
#objetivos .client-logo-frame {
  width: 160px; height: 60px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 4px;
  background: var(--blanco);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  padding: 8px 16px; overflow: hidden;
}
#objetivos .client-logo-frame img {
  max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; object-fit: contain;
}
#objetivos .client-logo-frame .logo-placeholder {
  font-family: var(--font-m); font-size: 8px;
  color: #bbb; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
}
#objetivos .client-name-tag {
  font-family: var(--font-m); font-size: 7px;
  color: #ccc; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding-top: 8px; width: 160px;
}
#objetivos .obj-pillars {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 1px; background: var(--border);
  width: 100%; max-width: 720px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
}
#objetivos .pillar {
  background: var(--blanco); padding: 28px 24px;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;
}
#objetivos .pillar-icon { color: var(--azul); --sz: 14px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
#objetivos .pillar-title { font-family: var(--font-b); font-weight: 700; font-size: 13px; color: var(--negro); letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
#objetivos .pillar-text { font-size: 12px; color: var(--gris); line-height: 1.6; }

/* ══════════════════════════════════════
   3. PROPUESTAS
══════════════════════════════════════ */
#propuestas {
  background: var(--blanco);
  align-items: center; padding: 80px 60px; min-height: 100vh;
}

#propuestas .prop-header {
  text-align: center; margin-bottom: 56px; width: 100%;
}
#propuestas .prop-label { color: var(--azul); margin-bottom: 14px; }
#propuestas h2 {
  font-family: var(--font-d);
  font-size: clamp(36px, 4.5vw, 58px);
  color: var(--negro); line-height: 0.95; letter-spacing: 0.02em;
}
#propuestas .prop-sub {
  margin-top: 10px; font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--gris); letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}

/* Cards */
.cards-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 1px; background: var(--border);
  width: 100%; max-width: 1100px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
}

.card {
  background: var(--blanco);
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; position: relative;
  transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease;
}
.card:hover { box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--azul); z-index: 1; }

.card-header {
  background: var(--azul); padding: 20px 24px 18px;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.card-header::after {
  content: ''; position: absolute; right: -10px; bottom: -10px;
  width: 50px; height: 50px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
}
.card-name {
  font-family: var(--font-b); font-weight: 700; font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--blanco); letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase;
}
.card-tagline {
  font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.4;
}

.card-body {
  padding: 24px; flex: 1;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px;
}

.card-section-label {
  font-family: var(--font-m); font-size: 7.5px; font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: var(--azul);
  text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px; display: block;
}

.card-items { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 7px; }
.card-items li {
  font-size: 12px; color: var(--negro); line-height: 1.45;
  padding-left: 14px; position: relative;
}
.card-items li::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 7px;
  width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--azul);
}
.card-items.excl li::before { background: var(--border); }
.card-items.excl li { color: var(--gris); }

.card-footer {
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 18px 24px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
}
.card-timeline { font-family: var(--font-m); font-size: 9px; color: var(--gris); letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
.card-price { font-family: var(--font-b); font-weight: 700; font-size: 20px; color: var(--azul); letter-spacing: 0.02em; }

/* ══════════════════════════════════════
   4. CONDICIONES
══════════════════════════════════════ */
#condiciones {
  background: var(--gris-cl);
  align-items: flex-start; padding: 100px 120px;
}

#condiciones .cond-label { color: var(--azul); margin-bottom: 20px; }
#condiciones h2 {
  font-family: var(--font-d);
  font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 54px);
  color: var(--negro); line-height: 0.95; margin-bottom: 48px;
}

/* Rectángulos horizontales apilados */
.cond-list {
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px;
  width: 100%; max-width: 800px;
}
.cond-item {
  background: var(--blanco);
  padding: 28px 32px;
  display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-start;
  border-left: 3px solid transparent;
  transition: border-color 0.2s;
}
.cond-item:hover { border-left-color: var(--azul); }

.cond-icon { color: var(--azul); --sz: 12px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 3px; }
.cond-content { flex: 1; }
.cond-title { font-weight: 700; font-size: 13px; color: var(--negro); margin-bottom: 6px; }
.cond-text { font-size: 12px; color: var(--gris); line-height: 1.65; }

.cond-note {
  margin-top: 36px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--gris);
  max-width: 640px; line-height: 1.7;
  padding-left: 16px; border-left: 2px solid var(--rojo);
}

/* ══════════════════════════════════════
   5. CONTACTO
══════════════════════════════════════ */
#contacto {
  background: var(--negro);
  min-height: 100vh; padding: 80px 120px 160px;
  justify-content: center; align-items: flex-start;
}

#contacto .close-star { position: absolute; right: 15%; top: 30%; color: var(--blanco); --sz: 32px; }
#contacto .close-star-sm { position: absolute; right: 28%; bottom: 28%; color: var(--lblue); --sz: 12px; }

#contacto .close-gradient {
  position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 3px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--naranja), var(--azul));
}

#contacto .close-label { color: var(--azul); margin-bottom: 24px; }

#contacto h2 {
  font-family: var(--font-d);
  font-size: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px);
  color: var(--blanco); line-height: 0.92;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em; margin-bottom: 56px;
}

.contact-block { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 56px; }
.contact-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
.contact-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--azul); flex-shrink: 0; }
.contact-label { font-family: var(--font-m); font-size: 9px; color: var(--gris); letter-spacing: 0.14em; width: 80px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.contact-value { font-family: var(--font-b); font-size: 14px; color: var(--blanco); font-weight: 400; }
.contact-value a { color: var(--blanco); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid #2a2a2a; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
.contact-value a:hover { border-color: var(--azul); }

#contacto .syur-footer {
  position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  background: var(--blanco); padding: 28px 0;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  border-top: 1px solid #efefef;
}
#contacto .syur-footer-logo {
  font-family: var(--font-d); font-size: 28px;
  color: var(--negro); letter-spacing: 0.12em;
}
#contacto .syur-footer-img {
  height: 44px; width: auto;
}

/* ══════════════════════════════════════
   RESPONSIVE — MOBILE ONLY
   Todo lo de abajo aplica ÚNICAMENTE en
   pantallas ≤ 768px. Desktop no se toca.
══════════════════════════════════════ */
@media (max-width: 768px) {

  /* Ocultar nav dots en mobile */
  .nav-dots { display: none; }

  /* Progress bar un poco más gruesa */
  .progress-bar { height: 3px; }

  /* ── CARÁTULA ── */
  #caratula {
    padding: 40px 28px 32px;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }
  #caratula .red-line { left: 28px; top: 6%; bottom: 6%; }
  #caratula .gradient-line { left: 28px; width: 70%; bottom: 18%; }
  #caratula .blue-block { opacity: 0.5; }
  #caratula .cover-content { padding-left: 20px; }
  #caratula h1 { font-size: clamp(48px, 13vw, 72px); }
  #caratula .year { font-size: 20px; }
  #caratula .cover-footer { padding-top: 16px; }

  /* ── OBJETIVOS ── */
  #objetivos {
    padding: 60px 28px 72px;
    min-height: auto;
  }
  #objetivos .obj-number { display: none; }
  #objetivos .obj-body { font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  #objetivos .obj-pillars {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    max-width: 100%;
  }
  #objetivos .client-logo-frame { margin-bottom: 4px; }

  /* ── PROPUESTAS ── */
  #propuestas {
    padding: 60px 20px 72px;
    min-height: auto;
  }
  #propuestas .prop-header { margin-bottom: 32px; }
  #propuestas h2 { font-size: clamp(32px, 9vw, 48px); }

  /* Cards: una debajo de la otra */
  .cards-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    max-width: 100%;
  }
  .card-price { font-size: 18px; }

  /* ── CONDICIONES ── */
  #condiciones {
    padding: 60px 24px 72px;
    min-height: auto;
  }
  #condiciones h2 { font-size: clamp(32px, 9vw, 48px); margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .cond-item { padding: 20px 20px; }

  /* ── CONTACTO ── */
  #contacto {
    padding: 60px 28px 140px;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }
  #contacto h2 { font-size: clamp(36px, 10vw, 60px); margin-bottom: 40px; }
  #contacto .close-star { display: none; }
  #contacto .close-star-sm { display: none; }
  .contact-label { width: 64px; font-size: 8px; }
  .contact-value { font-size: 13px; }
  #contacto .syur-footer { padding: 22px 0; }
  #contacto .syur-footer-img { height: 32px; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="progress-bar" id="progress"></div>

<nav class="nav-dots" id="navDots">
  <button class="nav-dot active" onclick="scrollTo('#caratula')" title="Carátula"></button>
  <button class="nav-dot" onclick="scrollTo('#objetivos')" title="Objetivos"></button>
  <button class="nav-dot" onclick="scrollTo('#propuestas')" title="Propuestas"></button>
  <button class="nav-dot" onclick="scrollTo('#condiciones')" title="Condiciones"></button>
  <button class="nav-dot" onclick="scrollTo('#contacto')" title="Contacto"></button>
</nav>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════
     1. CARÁTULA
══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="caratula">
  <div class="grain"></div>
  <div class="red-line"></div>
  <div class="blue-block"></div>
  <div class="gradient-line"></div>
  <div class="s1"><span class="star-shape"></span></div>
  <div class="s2"><span class="star-shape"></span></div>
  <div class="s3"><span class="star-shape"></span></div>

  <div class="cover-content">
    <div class="cover-label">PROPUESTA&nbsp;&nbsp;COMERCIAL</div>
    <h1>[NOMBRE DEL<br>PROYECTO]_</h1>
    <div class="year-row">
      <span class="year">2026</span>
      <div class="red-rule"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="cover-footer">
    <div class="cover-date">Marzo · 2026</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════
     2. OBJETIVOS
══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="objetivos">
  <div class="grain"></div>
  <div class="obj-red-accent"></div>
  <div class="obj-number">02</div>

  <div class="logos-row reveal">
    <div class="client-logo-frame">
      <!-- REEMPLAZAR con img src del logo del cliente -->
      <span class="logo-placeholder">Logo del cliente</span>
    </div>
    <span class="client-name-tag">[Nombre del proyecto]</span>
  </div>

  <div class="label obj-label reveal reveal-d1">02 — OBJETIVOS</div>

  <h2 class="reveal reveal-d2">Sobre este<br>proyecto_</h2>

  <p class="obj-body reveal reveal-d3">
    <!-- REEMPLAZAR con el objetivo del cliente — viene del output de ideación -->
    Diseñar la presentación oficial del Global Business Forum 2026, un evento de 3 días para 800 ejecutivos C-level. El objetivo es transmitir autoridad, escala global y claridad estratégica en cada slide — desde la apertura hasta el cierre de cada jornada.
  </p>

  <div class="obj-pillars reveal reveal-d4">
    <!-- PILARES: reemplazar con los 3 elegidos por Flor -->
    <div class="pillar">
      <span class="star-shape pillar-icon" style="--sz:12px; width:12px; height:12px;"></span>
      <div class="pillar-title">Autoridad</div>
      <div class="pillar-text">Cada pieza comunica liderazgo y expertise sin esfuerzo.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="pillar">
      <span class="star-shape pillar-icon" style="--sz:12px; width:12px; height:12px;"></span>
      <div class="pillar-title">Claridad</div>
      <div class="pillar-text">Mensajes que fluyen, conectan y se recuerdan.</div>
